{"tid":1896199,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"提提大家 新選民登記截止日期係5月2號","createTime":"2020-02-25T04:05:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T04:31:15.000Z","uid":226984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"db6cb67a958d2ef28999f2957d8f06cac2c82fc3","tid":1896199,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T04:05:53.000Z","msg":"根據選舉事務處資料，2020年選民登記周期法定限期如下:<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新登記申請：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2020年5月2日</span></span><br />\n更改登記資料申請：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2020年4月2日</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fvrsubmit.htm&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpXdxOOSMRKapPz%2BIyyZ8sYw%3D&h=1866955b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">留意:</span>只要你喺2020年7月25日或之前年滿十八歲，又是香港永久性居民，就符合資格，現在已可以申請登記做選民。)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，選舉事務處於2月5日起至4月期間按相關選舉法例陸續向約九萬名選民發出查訊信件，要求他們確認或更新其登記住址。如果有收到信，係需要喺<span style=\"color: red;\">5月2日或之前回覆</span>，否則會被納入在今年6月1日或之前發表的『取消登記名單』內。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202002/05/P2020020500513.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202002%2F05%2FP2020020500513.htm&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpXdxOOSMRKapPz%2BIyyZ8sYw%3D&h=39413cb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202002/05/P2020020500513.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n想知自己有冇被取消選民資格，自己click入選民資料網上查閱系統睇。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fweb%2F&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpXdxOOSMRKapPz%2BIyyZ8sYw%3D&h=892ba196\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n麻煩之前仲未登記選民嗰班朋友，盡一盡公民責任，登記番先。<br />\n登記左選民嘅，自己睇下有冇收到信。<br />\n<br />\n睇完依個post麻煩推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"070f706dd538b3b68c85643ae08633fbd7f69ceb","tid":1896199,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T04:07:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9a38e96893dcd89ec8393fa3d7c0ad19afd8e78","tid":1896199,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T04:07:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6a76005dd17a9f6a7f3e1a362c15651c9c90f0b","tid":1896199,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T04:07:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ffc73455cea43ff235e57d29c86bd6d85cc2c25","tid":1896199,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T04:11:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"78b8119a6301b4f5e2c2ef103bb9c3cb014cb39e","tid":1896199,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T04:31:15.000Z","msg":"推"}]}